 663        void CheckScreenSizeChanges()
 0664        {
 665            // We get a 5 pixel change in y height during initialization.
 666            // We could wait before considering size changes but using a delta is also useful
 0667            float sizeDeltaForChange = 10;
 668
 0669            Vector2 sizeDiff = position.size - m_LastScreenSize;
 0670            if (Math.Abs(sizeDiff.x) > sizeDeltaForChange || Math.Abs(sizeDiff.y) > sizeDeltaForChange)
 0671            {
 0672                if (m_LastScreenSize.x != 0) // At initialization time the screen size has not yet been recorded. Don't 
 0673                {
 0674                    m_LastScreenSize = position.size;
 0675                    if (!m_ScreenSizeChanged)
 0676                    {
 677                        // Record when we started the change
 0678                        m_ScreenSizeChanged = true;
 0679                        m_ScreenSizeChangedTimeStarted = EditorApplication.timeSinceStartup;
 0680                    }
 681                    // Record the last time of a change
 0682                    m_ScreenSizeChangedTimeFinished = EditorApplication.timeSinceStartup;
 683
 684                    // Record which tab we were on when it was changed
 0685                    m_ScreenSizeChangedTab = m_ActiveTab;
 0686                }
 0687            }
 688
 0689            if (m_ScreenSizeChanged)
 0690            {
 0691                double secondsSinceChanged = (EditorApplication.timeSinceStartup - m_ScreenSizeChangedTimeFinished);
 0692                double secondsToDelay = 3f;
 0693                if (secondsSinceChanged > secondsToDelay)
 0694                {
 695                    // Send analytic
 0696                    var uiResizeView = m_ScreenSizeChangedTab == ActiveTab.Summary ? ProfileAnalyzerAnalytics.UIResizeVi
 0697                    float durationInSeconds = (float)(m_ScreenSizeChangedTimeFinished - m_ScreenSizeChangedTimeStarted);
 0698                    ProfileAnalyzerAnalytics.SendUIResizeEvent(uiResizeView, durationInSeconds, position.size.x, positio
 699
 0700                    m_ScreenSizeChanged = false;
 0701                }
 0702            }
 0703        }

 710        void ProcessInput()
 0711        {
 0712            FrameTimeGraph.State inputStatus = FrameTimeGraph.State.None;
 713
 0714            if (m_ActiveTab == ActiveTab.Summary)
 0715            {
 0716                inputStatus = m_FrameTimeGraph.ProcessInput();
 0717            }
 0718            else if (m_ActiveTab == ActiveTab.Compare)
 0719            {
 0720                if (m_ProfileLeftView.IsDataValid() && inputStatus == FrameTimeGraph.State.None)
 0721                    inputStatus = m_LeftFrameTimeGraph.ProcessInput();
 722
 0723                if (m_ProfileRightView.IsDataValid() && inputStatus == FrameTimeGraph.State.None)
 0724                    inputStatus = m_RightFrameTimeGraph.ProcessInput();
 0725            }
 726
 0727            switch (inputStatus)
 728            {
 729                case FrameTimeGraph.State.Dragging:
 0730                    m_RequestRepaint = true;
 0731                    break;
 732                case FrameTimeGraph.State.DragComplete:
 0733                    m_RequestCompare = true;
 0734                    break;
 735            }
 736
 0737            if (Event.current.isKey && Event.current.type == EventType.KeyDown)
 0738            {
 0739                switch (Event.current.keyCode)
 740                {
 741                    case KeyCode.Alpha1:
 0742                        if (m_ActiveTab == ActiveTab.Summary)

 1667        internal int CompareUINames(string a, string b)
 01668        {
 01669            var aSpaceIndex = a.LastIndexOf(' ');
 01670            var bSpaceIndex = b.LastIndexOf(' ');
 1671
 01672            if (aSpaceIndex >= 0 && bSpaceIndex >= 0)
 01673            {
 01674                var aThreadName = a.Substring(0, aSpaceIndex);
 01675                var bThreadName = b.Substring(0, bSpaceIndex);
 1676
 01677                if (aThreadName == bThreadName)
 01678                {
 01679                    var aThreadIndex = a.Substring(aSpaceIndex + 1);
 01680                    var bThreadIndex = b.Substring(bSpaceIndex + 1);
 1681
 01682                    if (aThreadIndex == "All" && bThreadIndex != "All")
 01683                        return -1;
 01684                    if (aThreadIndex != "All" && bThreadIndex == "All")
 01685                        return 1;
 1686
 1687                    int aGroupIndex;
 01688                    if (int.TryParse(aThreadIndex, out aGroupIndex))
 01689                    {
 1690                        int bGroupIndex;
 01691                        if (int.TryParse(bThreadIndex, out bGroupIndex))
 01692                        {
 01693                            return aGroupIndex.CompareTo(bGroupIndex);
 1694                        }
 01695                    }
 01696                }
 01697            }
 1698
 01699            return a.CompareTo(b);
 01700        }

 1957        static List<string> GetNameFilters(string nameFilter)
 01958        {
 01959            List<string> nameFilters = new List<string>();
 01960            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(nameFilter))
 01961                return nameFilters;
 1962
 1963            // Get all quoted strings, without the quotes
 01964            MatchCollection matches = quotedStringWithoutQuotes.Matches(nameFilter);
 01965            foreach (Match match in matches)
 01966            {
 01967                var theData = match.Groups[1].Value;
 01968                nameFilters.Add(theData);
 01969            }
 1970
 1971            // Get a new string with the quoted strings removed
 01972            string remaining = quotedString.Replace(nameFilter, "");
 1973
 1974            // Get all the remaining strings (that are space separated)
 01975            matches = stringWithoutWhiteSpace.Matches(remaining);
 01976            foreach (Match match in matches)
 01977            {
 01978                string theData = match.Groups[1].Value;
 01979                nameFilters.Add(theData);
 01980            }
 1981
 01982            return nameFilters;
 01983        }

 2462        bool UpdateDepthFilters()
 02463        {
 02464            bool changed = false;
 2465
 02466            if (m_ActiveTab == ActiveTab.Compare)
 02467            {
 2468                // First respect the auto flag
 02469                if (UpdateAutoDepthFilter())
 02470                    changed = true;
 2471
 2472                // Make sure Single matches the updated comparison view
 02473                if (m_ProfileLeftView.path == m_ProfileSingleView.path)
 02474                {
 2475                    // Use same filter on single view if its the same file
 02476                    if (m_DepthFilter != m_DepthFilter1)
 02477                    {
 02478                        m_DepthFilter = m_DepthFilter1;
 02479                        changed = true;
 02480                    }
 02481                }
 02482                if (m_ProfileRightView.path == m_ProfileSingleView.path)
 02483                {
 2484                    // Use same filter on single view if its the same file
 02485                    if (m_DepthFilter != m_DepthFilter2)
 02486                    {
 02487                        m_DepthFilter = m_DepthFilter2;
 02488                        changed = true;
 02489                    }
 02490                }
 02491            }
 2492            else
 02493            {
 2494                // Make sure comparisons match updated single view
 2495
 02496                if (m_ProfileLeftView.path == m_ProfileSingleView.path)
 02497                {
 2498                    // Use same filter on comparison left view if its the same file
 02499                    if (m_DepthFilter1 != m_DepthFilter)
 02500                    {
 02501                        m_DepthFilter1 = m_DepthFilter;
 02502                        changed = true;
 02503                    }
 2504
 02505                    if (UpdateAutoDepthFilter())
 02506                        changed = true;
 02507                }
 2508
 02509                if (m_ProfileRightView.path == m_ProfileSingleView.path)
 02510                {
 2511                    // Use same filter on comparison right view if its the same file
 02512                    if (m_DepthFilter2Auto)
 02513                    {
 2514                        // When auto selected we have to set the left filter to new depth - diff
 02515                        int newDepthFilter1 = (m_DepthFilter == ProfileAnalyzer.kDepthAll) ? ProfileAnalyzer.kDepthAll :
 02516                        if (m_DepthFilter1 != newDepthFilter1)
 02517                        {
 02518                            m_DepthFilter1 = newDepthFilter1;
 02519                            changed = true;
 02520                        }
 2521
 02522                        if (UpdateAutoDepthFilter())
 02523                            changed = true;
 02524                    }
 2525                    else
 02526                    {
 02527                        if (m_DepthFilter2 != m_DepthFilter)
 02528                        {
 02529                            m_DepthFilter2 = m_DepthFilter;

 02531                        }
 02532                    }
 02533                }
 02534            }
 2535
 02536            return changed;
 02537        }

 2546        string CalculateSelectedThreadsSummary()
 02547        {
 02548            if (m_ThreadSelection.selection == null || m_ThreadSelection.selection.Count == 0)
 02549                return "None";
 2550
 2551            // Count all threads in a group
 02552            var threadDict = new Dictionary<string, int>();
 02553            var threadSelectionDict = new Dictionary<string, int>();
 02554            foreach (var threadNameWithIndex in m_ThreadNames)
 02555            {
 02556                var threadIdentifier = new ThreadIdentifier(threadNameWithIndex);
 02557                if (threadIdentifier.index == ThreadIdentifier.kAll)
 02558                    continue;
 2559
 2560                int count;
 02561                if (threadDict.TryGetValue(threadIdentifier.name, out count))
 02562                    threadDict[threadIdentifier.name] = count + 1;
 2563                else
 02564                    threadDict[threadIdentifier.name] = 1;
 2565
 02566                threadSelectionDict[threadIdentifier.name] = 0;
 02567            }
 2568
 2569            // Count all the threads we have 'selected' in a group
 02570            foreach (var threadNameWithIndex in m_ThreadSelection.selection)
 02571            {
 02572                var threadIdentifier = new ThreadIdentifier(threadNameWithIndex);
 2573
 02574                if (threadDict.ContainsKey(threadIdentifier.name) &&
 2575                    threadSelectionDict.ContainsKey(threadIdentifier.name) &&
 2576                    threadIdentifier.index <= threadDict[threadIdentifier.name])
 02577                {
 2578                    // Selected thread valid and in the thread list
 2579                    // and also within the range of valid threads for this data set
 02580                    threadSelectionDict[threadIdentifier.name]++;
 02581                }
 02582            }
 2583
 2584            // Count all thread groups where we have 'selected all the threads'
 02585            int threadsSelected = 0;
 02586            foreach (var threadName in threadDict.Keys)
 02587            {
 02588                if (threadSelectionDict[threadName] != threadDict[threadName])
 02589                    continue;
 2590
 02591                threadsSelected++;
 02592            }
 2593
 2594            // If we've just added all the thread names we have everything selected
 2595            // Note we don't compare against the m_ThreadNames directly as this contains the 'all' versions
 02596            if (threadsSelected == threadDict.Keys.Count)
 02597                return "All";
 2598
 2599            // Add all the individual threads were we haven't already added the group
 02600            List<string> threads = new List<string>();
 02601            foreach (var threadName in threadSelectionDict.Keys)
 02602            {
 02603                int selectionCount = threadSelectionDict[threadName];
 02604                if (selectionCount <= 0)
 02605                    continue;
 02606                int threadCount = threadDict[threadName];
 02607                if (threadCount == 1)
 02608                    threads.Add(threadName);
 02609                else if (selectionCount != threadCount)
 02610                    threads.Add(string.Format("{0} ({1} of {2})", threadName, selectionCount, threadCount));
 2611                else
 02612                    threads.Add(string.Format("{0} (All)", threadName));
 02613            }
 2614
 2615            // Maintain alphabetical order
 02616            threads.Sort(CompareUINames);
 2617
 02618            if (threads.Count == 0)
 02619                return "None";
 2620
 02621            string threadsSelectedText = string.Join(", ", threads.ToArray());
 02622            return threadsSelectedText;
 02623        }
 2624

 02627            return m_ThreadSelectionSummary;
 02628        }

 2902        enum InDataSet
 2903        {
 2904            Left,
 2905            Both,
 2906            Right
 2907        };
 2908
 2909        int GetCombinedThreadCount(out int matchingCount, out int uniqueLeft, out int uniqueRight)
 02910        {
 02911            var threads = new Dictionary<string, InDataSet>();
 02912            foreach (var threadName in m_ProfileLeftView.data.GetThreadNames())
 02913            {
 02914                threads[threadName] = InDataSet.Left;
 02915            }
 02916            foreach (var threadName in m_ProfileRightView.data.GetThreadNames())
 02917            {
 02918                if (threads.ContainsKey(threadName))
 02919                    threads[threadName] = InDataSet.Both;
 2920                else
 02921                    threads[threadName] = InDataSet.Right;
 02922            }
 2923
 02924            matchingCount = 0;
 02925            uniqueLeft = 0;
 02926            uniqueRight = 0;
 02927            int total = 0;
 02928            foreach (var thread in threads)
 02929            {
 02930                switch (thread.Value)
 2931                {
 2932                    case InDataSet.Left:
 02933                        uniqueLeft++;
 02934                        break;
 2935                    case InDataSet.Both:
 02936                        matchingCount++;
 02937                        break;
 2938                    case InDataSet.Right:
 02939                        uniqueRight++;
 02940                        break;
 2941                }
 02942                total++;
 02943            }
 2944
 02945            return total;
 02946        }

 3106        bool IsAnalysisValid(bool checkFrameCount = false)
 03107        {

 3109            {
 3110                case ActiveTab.Summary:
 03111                    if (!m_ProfileSingleView.IsDataValid())
 03112                        return false;
 3113
 03114                    if (m_ProfileSingleView.analysis == null)
 03115                        return false;
 3116
 03117                    if (checkFrameCount)
 03118                    {
 03119                        if (m_ProfileSingleView.analysis.GetFrameSummary().frames.Count <= 0)
 03120                            return false;
 03121                    }
 03122                    break;
 3123
 3124                case ActiveTab.Compare:
 03125                    if (!m_ProfileLeftView.IsDataValid())
 03126                        return false;
 03127                    if (!m_ProfileRightView.IsDataValid())
 03128                        return false;
 3129
 03130                    if (m_ProfileLeftView.analysis == null)
 03131                        return false;
 03132                    if (m_ProfileRightView.analysis == null)
 03133                        return false;
 3134
 03135                    if (checkFrameCount)
 03136                    {
 03137                        if (m_ProfileLeftView.analysis.GetFrameSummary().frames.Count <= 0)
 03138                            return false;
 03139                        if (m_ProfileRightView.analysis.GetFrameSummary().frames.Count <= 0)
 03140                            return false;
 03141                    }
 03142                    break;
 3143            }
 3144
 3145            //if (IsAnalysisRunning())
 3146            //    return false;
 3147
 03148            return true;
 03149        }

 3588        void DrawComparisonHistogram(float height, float minValue, float maxValue, int bucketCount, int[] leftBuckets, i
 03589        {
 03590            Histogram histogram = new Histogram(m_2D, displayUnits.Units);
 03591            float width = LayoutSize.HistogramWidth;
 03592            float min = minValue;
 03593            float max = maxValue;
 03594            float spacing = 2;
 3595
 03596            float range = max - min;
 3597            // bucketCount = (range == 0f) ? 1 : bucketCount;
 3598
 03599            float x = (spacing / 2);
 03600            float y = 0;
 03601            float w = ((width + spacing) / bucketCount) - spacing;
 03602            float h = height;
 3603
 03604            histogram.DrawStart(width);
 3605
 03606            if (m_2D.DrawStart(width, height, Draw2D.Origin.BottomLeft))
 03607            {
 03608                float bucketWidth = (range / bucketCount);
 03609                Rect rect = GUILayoutUtility.GetLastRect();
 3610
 03611                histogram.DrawBackground(width, height, bucketCount, min, max, spacing);
 3612
 03613                if (!IsAnalysisRunning())
 03614                {
 03615                    for (int bucketAt = 0; bucketAt < bucketCount; bucketAt++)
 03616                    {
 03617                        float leftBarCount = leftValid ? leftBuckets[bucketAt] : 0;
 03618                        float rightBarCount = rightValid ? rightBuckets[bucketAt] : 0;
 03619                        float leftBarHeight = leftValid ? ((h * leftBarCount) / leftCount) : 0;
 03620                        float rightBarHeight = rightValid ? ((h * rightBarCount) / rightCount) : 0;
 3621
 03622                        if (leftBarCount > 0)  // Make sure we always slow a small bar if non zero
 03623                            leftBarHeight = Mathf.Max(1.0f, leftBarHeight);
 03624                        if (rightBarCount > 0)  // Make sure we always slow a small bar if non zero
 03625                            rightBarHeight = Mathf.Max(1.0f, rightBarHeight);
 3626
 03627                        if ((int)rightBarHeight == (int)leftBarHeight)
 03628                        {
 03629                            m_2D.DrawFilledBox(x, y, w, leftBarHeight, UIColor.both);
 03630                        }
 03631                        else if (rightBarHeight > leftBarHeight)
 03632                        {
 03633                            m_2D.DrawFilledBox(x, y, w, rightBarHeight, UIColor.right);
 03634                            m_2D.DrawFilledBox(x, y, w, leftBarHeight, UIColor.both);
 03635                        }
 3636                        else
 03637                        {
 03638                            m_2D.DrawFilledBox(x, y, w, leftBarHeight, UIColor.left);
 03639                            m_2D.DrawFilledBox(x, y, w, rightBarHeight, UIColor.both);
 03640                        }
 3641
 03642                        float bucketStart = min + (bucketAt * bucketWidth);
 03643                        float bucketEnd = bucketStart + bucketWidth;
 3644
 03645                        string tooltip = string.Format(
 3646                            "{0}-{1}\nLeft: {2} {3}\nRight: {4} {5}\n\nBar width: {6}",
 3647                            displayUnits.ToString(bucketStart, false, 5),
 3648                            displayUnits.ToString(bucketEnd, true, 5),
 3649                            leftBarCount, leftBarCount == 1 ? "frame" : "frames",

 3763        float GetThreadTimeRange(ProfileAnalysis profileAnalysis)
 03764        {
 03765            if (profileAnalysis == null)
 03766                return 0.0f;
 3767
 03768            var frameSummary = profileAnalysis.GetFrameSummary();
 03769            float range = frameSummary.msMax;
 03770            switch (m_ThreadRange)
 3771            {
 3772                case ThreadRange.Median:
 03773                    range = frameSummary.msMedian;
 03774                    break;
 3775                case ThreadRange.UpperQuartile:
 03776                    range = frameSummary.msUpperQuartile;
 03777                    break;
 3778                case ThreadRange.Max:
 03779                    range = frameSummary.msMax;
 03780                    break;
 3781            }
 3782
 03783            return range;
 03784        }

 3786        int GetThreadSelectionCount(out int leftSelectionCount, out int rightSelectionCount)
 03787        {
 03788            List<string> threadSelection = GetLimitedThreadSelection(m_ThreadNames, m_ThreadSelection);
 03789            leftSelectionCount = 0;
 03790            foreach (var threadName in m_ProfileLeftView.data.GetThreadNames())
 03791            {
 03792                if (threadSelection.Contains(threadName))
 03793                {
 03794                    leftSelectionCount++;
 03795                }
 03796            }
 03797            rightSelectionCount = 0;
 03798            foreach (var threadName in m_ProfileRightView.data.GetThreadNames())
 03799            {
 03800                if (threadSelection.Contains(threadName))
 03801                {
 03802                    rightSelectionCount++;
 03803                }
 03804            }
 03805            return threadSelection.Count;
 03806        }

 4482        internal void SelectMarkerByIndex(int index)

 04502                        valid = false;

 4504

 04509                        valid = false;
 04510                }
 04511            }

 04513            m_SelectedMarker = index;
 4514

 04516            {
 04517                List<int> selection = new List<int>();
 04518                if (index >= 0 && valid)

 4564        internal void SelectPairing(int index)
 04565        {
 04566            if (m_Pairings == null || m_Pairings.Count==0)
 04567                return;
 4568
 4569            // Check if this marker is in the 'filtered' list
 04570            bool valid = true;
 04571            if (index >= 0 && index < m_Pairings.Count)
 04572            {
 04573                var pairing = m_Pairings[index];
 4574
 04575                var nameFilters = GetNameFilters();
 04576                if (nameFilters.Count > 0)
 04577                {
 04578                    if (!NameInFilterList(pairing.name, nameFilters))
 04579                        valid = false;
 04580                }
 4581
 04582                var nameExcludes = GetNameExcludes();
 04583                if (nameExcludes.Count > 0)
 04584                {
 04585                    if (NameInExcludeList(pairing.name, nameExcludes))
 04586                        valid = false;
 04587                }
 04588            }
 4589
 04590            m_SelectedPairing = index;
 4591
 04592            if (m_ComparisonTable != null)
 04593            {
 04594                List<int> selection = new List<int>();
 04595                if (index >= 0 && valid)
 04596                    selection.Add(index);
 04597                m_ComparisonTable.SetSelection(selection, TreeViewSelectionOptions.RevealAndFrame);
 04598            }
 4599
 04600            var markerName = GetPairingName(index);
 04601            if (markerName!=null)
 04602                UpdateSelectedMarkerName(markerName);
 04603        }
